import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import Vuex from 'vuex'
import store from './store/in.js'
import VueRouter from './router/index'

Vue.use(Vuex)
Vue.config.productionTip = false

const vueStore = new Vuex.Store(store)
new Vue({
  router:VueRouter,
  store:vueStore,
  render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app')
